ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectThe Harrison Hot Springs Chamber of Commerce (British Columbia) ** Change of Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the HARRISON HOT SPRINGS CHAMBER OF COMMERCE, in British Columbia, TO CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES OF ITS DISTRICT from the Village of Harrison Hot Springs and surrounding area to the Village of Harrison Hot Springs and the District of Kent.
